title: 5780 HD Anime Wallpapers [Bluntjoker]
description:
If you've been following my wallpaper releases, this one may surprise you at 18GB's. Quality is through the roof on this one, images with artifacts are kept to a minimum.


All images are at least 1920x1080p with many much larger sizes up to 20000px wide.


This time I've included Vectors, Hatsune Miku, .gif's, and much more!


5,780 wallpapers in total.
